## Final report

### Source changes
**None.** `src/lib.rs` is identical to the baseline. All 5 unit tests pass (`run_cargo_test` ok at the end).

### Hax / lake build errors driving the analysis
1. `run_cargo_hax_into_lean` → **`[HAX0001] Unsupported equality constraints on associated types of parent trait`** (issue #1923), Lean Printer context, spanning the entire `pub fn map_fold(...) { ... }` body.
